	var healthFinding = request.pathParams.finding;

		patterns.push({
            state: HealthTrackerInterrogate.getDisplayValue('state'),
			ignore_reason: HealthTrackerInterrogate.getValue('ignore_reason'),

        });
			
			//Continuned code
			
		}else{
			
			patterns.push({
            error: 'NO Scan has been Run on offending Update set',
